<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-16 14:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3556 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v BC-SPOT-BJT17-COX     07-16 1111
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT17-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
