get a gift certificate for $10 at Gap.com. Spend $40 at Gap.com and
you get a $10 gift certificate at ProFlowers.com. Or, buy something
at Barnes&AMP;Noble.com and you get a 10 percent discount at
1-800-Flowers.com. The name of the game is reciprocal marketing,
and more and more e-commerce companies are turning to it. By Bob
Tedeschi.
</P>
<P>
   PATENTS (Undated) _ A Web site for cargo rates lays claim to a
business method, entering a gray area of the law. By Sabra
Chartrand.
</P>
<P>
   BIZGLANCE (Undated) _ Major financial stories at a glance.
</P>
<P>
   ECON-CALENDAR (Undated) _ Key government figures this week.
</P>
<P>
   BOND-CALENDAR (Undated) _ The week's planned offerings.
</P>
<P>
   EQUITIES (Undated) _ Equity issues coming to market this week.
</P>
<P>
   DIVIDEND-MEETINGS (Undated) _ Major meetings this week.
