this week's Davis Cup, claiming a back injury suffered when his car
was rear-ended in Las Vegas the day he got back from Wimbledon.
</P>
<P>
   ``There was a lot of damage, not just to my car but apparently
to my back,'' Agassi told Jim Rome on his radio show Friday.
</P>
<P>
   So why didn't he fill out a police report? Agassi said: ``I
actually know the person, and it wasn't my intention to take this
any further.''
</P>
<P>
