with 23-year-old Playboy playmate Darlene Bernaola (she was co-Miss
January, with her twin sister, Carol), and he intends to keep it
low-key.
</P>
<P>
   Just like every other guy in America would do if he was dating a
freak'n centerfold. ...
</P>
