scholarship to San Diego State.
</P>
<P>
   Then, for some crazy reason, she transferred to UCLA 'cause she
wanted to start ``a lucrative modeling and acting career'' (that,
taken verbatim from her Playmate data sheet).
</P>
<P>
   So volleyball's loss is ... well, ya know ...
</P>
