<P>
   E-COMMERCE-COLUMN (Undated) _ Go to eToys and spend $40, and you
get a gift certificate for $10 at Gap.com. Spend $40 at Gap.com and
you get a $10 gift certificate at ProFlowers.com. Or, buy something
at Barnes&AMP;Noble.com and you get a 10 percent discount at
1-800-Flowers.com. The name of the game is reciprocal marketing,
and more and more e-commerce companies are turning to it. By Bob
Tedeschi.
